name: Forest Fire
prepTime: 1 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (3/2 oz)	Rye
  - (1/3 oz)	Pine Liqueur
  - (1/3 oz)	Sweet Vermouth
  - (3 dashes)	Snappy's Firewater
  - (3 drops)	Devil's Larder Smoke Bitters
  - (2 pieces)	Cedar wood	

steps:
  - Light first cedar piece, and set on aluminum
  - Place (chilled) glass facedown over lit cedar, to smoke the glass
  - After 20-30s, turn glass upright, and pour in ingredients
  - Mix, then light the other cedar piece, and toss in to extinguish
